Exception Summary
SearchEngineException An exception that indicates that an error occurred when querying a search engine.
SearchEngineFatalException An exception that indicates that a fatal error occurred when querying a search engine, and therefore the query should not be retried.
SearchEngineQuotaException An exception that indicates the quota for the (rate-limited) allowable number of queries has been exceeded.
 

Package sg.yeefan.searchenginewrapper Description

Provides a wrapper framework for unifying programatic access to search engines.

The main class for this package is SearchEngineWrapper, to be used in conjunction with one of the search engine clients subclassed from SearchEngineClient or KeyedSearchEngineClient.

Tan Yee Fan
